nh\u00e0. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean hay nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o th\u00ec c\u00f9ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 tr\u1ee3 l\u1eabn nhau trong kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"614\" class=\"wp-image-10907\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11-1024x614.gif\" alt=\"hieu-ung-anh-sang-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11-1024x614.gif 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11-300x180.gif 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11-768x461.gif 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11-1536x922.gif 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11-2048x1229.gif 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/strong><\/h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng; c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ch\u1ecbu t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd t\u1eeb \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o. Khi x\u00e9t theo t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t, \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i theo chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfu tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng t\u00ednh to\u00e1n k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u1ec1 b\u1ed1 c\u1ee5c s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n; thi\u1ebfu c\u1ea3m x\u00fac cho kh\u00f4ng gian. C\u00f2n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng th\u1ecb gi\u00e1c m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac cho kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft t\u1edbi nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c khe s\u00e1ng, \u00f4 s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp.<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"563\" class=\"wp-image-10908\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/2-1024x563.jpg\" alt=\"hieu-ung-anh-sang-trong-thiet-ke-noi-that\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/2-1024x563.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/2-300x165.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/2-768x422.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/2-1536x845.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/2-2048x1126.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/2.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Theo m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch, \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia l\u00e0m 3 lo\u1ea1i g\u1ed3m: \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng ch\u00fang; \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng trang tr\u00ed.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\r\n<li>\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng chung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1eddng hi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng chi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec1u, d\u00e0n tr\u1ea3i kh\u1eafp kh\u00f4ng gian. Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng chung c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng theo v\u00f9ng; theo \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 sinh ho\u1ea1t.\u00a0<\/li>\r\n<li>\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1eadp trung t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n; qua \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng. Nh\u1edd \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1eadp trung, ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n v\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng gian cho nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian m\u1edf trong phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng &#8211; t\u1ed1i l\u00e0 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng t\u1eadp trung.\u00a0<\/li>\r\n<li>M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u00f4ng n\u0103ng; nh\u01b0ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng trang tr\u00ed l\u1ea1i l\u00e0m t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t; gi\u00fap t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng th\u1ecb gi\u00e1c g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd.\u00a0<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n v\u00e0 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc song song v\u1edbi qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;<\/p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/\"><strong>Byzan Interior Design <\/strong><\/a>&#8211; th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u m\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch Hi\u1ec7n \u011